cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

The paper deals with optimisation of classifiers using genetic algorithms, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus is on image recognition, which suggests the computer vision sub-category (cs.CV). The use of feature reduction is also mentioned, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the use of genetic algorithms for optimisation is a common topic in neural networks and evolutionary algorithms (cs.NE).
